  "core_payload": {
    "content_type": "markdown",
    "content": "# Daily Planner Agent\n\n## 1. Role\nDaily Planner Agent will become the adaptive short-horizon planner that continuously compresses the larger planning field into grounded plans for today, tomorrow, and the immediate week.\n\n## 2. Future Daily Planning Contract\nThe agent will reshape near-horizon work from execution evidence, reminders, risk signals, branch posture, and realistic capacity instead of from static task lists. It will explain why one item deserves today, why another should wait, and what changed when the daily field is re-cut.\n\n## 3. Operational Consequence\nDaily planning will become more responsive to real human load, missed work, changing urgency, and new evidence from the graph. Strategy will stay livable at day scale because the short horizon will update without losing alignment with the roadmap.\n\n## 4. Philosophical Alignment\nDaily Planner Agent supports To Dig Deep by turning strategy into disciplined present-tense action at the scale of real days."
  },
